OL,7,FThe family of the young person that
OL,8,Fwas allegedly paid for explicit sexual
OL,9,Fphotos by the former BBC broadcaster
OL,10,FHuw Edwards say they doubt that he
OL,11,Fwill return his salary.
OL,13,FOn Friday, the corporation said the
OL,14,FBBC board has "authorised the
OL,15,Fexecutive to seek the return" of
OL,16,FEdwards payments from his November
OL,17,Farrest to April, when the 62-year-old
OL,18,Fresigned on medical advice.
