OL,7,FLast year, a separate allegation in
OL,8,Fthe Sun saw Edwards accused of paying
OL,9,Fa teenager #35,000 for photos, and he
OL,10,Fwas later named as the BBC presenter
OL,11,Fat the centre of the media furore.
OL,13,FThe family of the unnamed young person
OL,14,Foriginally complained to the BBC in
OL,15,FMay 2023, and the corporation
OL,16,Fapologised earlier this year over the
OL,17,Fhandling of the complaint.
