OL,7,FThe young person's stepfather told
OL,8,FSaturday's edition of the Sun: "He
OL,9,Fshouldn't have been paid when
OL,10,Fsuspended, let alone being paid for
OL,11,Ffive months more after they knew he
OL,12,Fhad been arrested.
OL,14,F"It's immoral. I don't think he will
OL,15,Fwillingly pay it back though."
OL,17,FThe stepfather previously shared a
OL,18,Fvideo with the newspaper that he
OL,19,Ffilmed of Edwards waiting for the
OL,20,Falleged victim at a Welsh train
OL,21,Fstation.
