OL,7,FPolice found no evidence of criminal
OL,8,Fbehaviour in the matter.
OL,10,FThe unnamed teenager told the Mirror
OL,11,Fnewspaper this month that he felt
OL,12,F"groomed" by the broadcaster and
OL,13,F"sick" after learning he was charged
OL,14,Fwith child sex crimes.
OL,16,FIn July, a court heard Edwards had
OL,17,Fbeen involved in an online chat with
OL,18,Fan adult man on WhatsApp between
OL,19,FDecember 2020 and August 2021, who
OL,20,Fsent him 377 sexual images, of which
OL,21,F41 were indecent images of children.
