OL,7,FA statement from the BBC on Friday
OL,8,Fsaid: "Whilst the nature of the
OL,9,Fcharges against Mr Edwards is related
OL,10,Fto his own personal life, the board
OL,11,Fbelieves these events have also put a
OL,12,Fspotlight on the question of power
OL,13,Fimbalances in the workplace.
OL,15,F"We remain concerned about the
OL,16,Fpotential for inappropriate workplace
OL,17,Fbehaviour, particularly in creative
OL,18,Fand editorial environments.
