OL,10,FBBC must hold itself to the highest
OL,11,Fstandards."
OL,13,FIt also announced the board has
OL,14,Fcommissioned an independent review
OL,15,Fthat will "make recommendations on
OL,16,Fpractical steps that could strengthen
OL,17,Fa workplace culture in line with BBC
OL,18,Fvalues" .
