OL,7,FThe corporation will set out terms of
OL,8,Freference and leadership of this
OL,9,Freview in early September.
OL,11,FThe Culture Secretary Lisa Nandy, who
OL,12,Fpreviously called for Edwards to
OL,13,Freturn his salary, welcomed the
OL,14,Findependent review, and said: "BBC
OL,15,Fstaff must be able to feel safe in the
OL,16,Fworkplace and be confident that if non-
OL,17,Feditorial complaints are raised they
OL,18,Fwill be acted upon and dealt with
OL,19,Ffairly and decisively."
